Variable Description: Percent of children aged 0-6 with confirmed blood lead level  >= 5.0 μg/dL
Formula: Number of children aged 0-6 with confirmed blood lead level  >= 5.0 μg/dL  /  Number of children aged 0-6 tested for blood lead level

Variable Description: Five year average - Percent of children aged 0-6 with confirmed blood lead level >= 5.0 μg/dL
Formula: (Sum of percent of children aged 0-6 with confirmed blood lead level  >= 5.0 μg/dL  from 2010 to 2014 ) / 5
